short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get prettier, more readable USACO Solutions!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension automatically adds code syntax highlighting to USACO solution pages, making them easier to read and understand. You can also choose whether you want it to be in dark (default), or light mode! It auto detects whether the solution code is in C++, Java, or Python and applies the appropriate highlighting. Enjoy!
